    public class EngineeredCapabilityImpl
extends CapabilityImpl
implements EngineeredCapability
    An implementation of the model object 'Engineered Capability'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Aligns
    • Completion
    • Benefit
    • Total Cost
    • Assignee
    • All Issues
    • Capacity
    • Objectives
    • Linked Objectives
    • All Objectives
    • Affects
    • Releases
